"paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn78:13.20"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ paṭipanno kho, thapati, kusalānaṃ saṅkappānaṃ nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:14.1"
msgid ""
"Katamehi cāhaṃ, thapati, dasahi dhammehi samannāgataṃ purisapuggalaṃ "
"paññapemi sampannakusalaṃ paramakusalaṃ uttamapattipattaṃ samaṇaṃ ayojjhaṃ?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn78:14.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, thapati, bhikkhu asekhāya sammādiṭṭhiyā samannāgato hoti, asekhena "
"sammāsaṅkappena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāvācāya samannāgato hoti, "
"asekhena sammākammantena samannāgato hoti, asekhena sammāājīvena samannāgato "
"hoti, asekhena sammāvāyāmena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāsatiyā "
"samannāgato hoti, asekhena sammāsamādhinā samannāgato hoti, asekhena "
"sammāñāṇena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāvimuttiyā samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn78:14.3"
msgid ""
"imehi kho ahaṃ, thapati, dasahi dhammehi samannāgataṃ purisapuggalaṃ "
"paññapemi sampannakusalaṃ paramakusalaṃ uttamapattipattaṃ samaṇaṃ "
"ayojjhan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:14.4"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn78:14.5"
msgid "Attamano pañcakaṅgo thapati bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn78:14.6"
msgid "Samaṇamuṇḍikasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
